{"tid":2458283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭定康：《基本法》畢竟是一份中國的文件，它與《聯合聲明》矛盾","createTime":"2021-03-23T09:58:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T11:14:11.000Z","uid":261647,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1592296aeb9f5a34eeb5f8f0dbada7ca219b850a","tid":2458283,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T09:58:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/recall.hk/posts/2916441838677855\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frecall.hk%2Fposts%2F2916441838677855&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97Yc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=bdc9b1ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/recall.hk/posts/2916441838677855</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：世代懺悔錄：香港前途考古札記<br />\n<br />\n彭定康口述，《說吧，香港》(1999) 259&ndash;260：<br />\n//我考慮的是一個關鍵的問題是：《聯合聲明》要如實地執行，而不是將它重新詮釋才實行&hellip;你說的是選舉，即人們走進投票站公正地投票，還是秘密地安排一切？雖然《基本法》嘗試反映《聯合聲明》的精神，它畢竟是一份中國的文件，它與《聯合聲明》的矛盾，應由中方處理&hellip;"},{"pid":"353e108916efae56c33cb8126f733620ca73ead1","tid":2458283,"uid":279463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T10:00:19.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"69e41e5328078ca144d7e6c110b7571d3baf759b","tid":2458283,"uid":39653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:14:11.000Z","msg":"民主回歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}